{"tid":2352114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做gym 既你平時出街有咩野食方便買又入到口？","createTime":"2021-01-03T18:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T19:57:21.000Z","uid":290353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00b0361ad831c4a7caf9bdb3861f1160f76e33e2","tid":2352114,"uid":290353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"唔想餐餐都譚仔雞肉清湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩開始做gym 冇耐<br />\n屋企有小量器材舉下野咁<br />\n唔專業 <br />\n依家都希望從出街飲食著手<br />\n有時拍拖好難另一半就哂你 餐餐譚仔 都怕佢食到悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有巴絲指導下 求改善自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60116e68c2681b26d9e275f795e2832a80b1d29e","tid":2352114,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:48:17.000Z","msg":"譚仔雞肉清湯<br />\n<br />\n味精多到你舉一世都無效果啦.."},{"pid":"bc6bde0d54ab9793d664ea7b8172b78cad180a90","tid":2352114,"uid":73066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"鋸扒走汁<br />\n神石燒<br />\n大快活雞胸<br />\n<br />\n不過你要拍拖一個星期最多咪兩日<br />\n咁你平時果五日返屋企食雞柳囉"},{"pid":"d5053721339bdac92f368b52ce5a9ab3a9a765a1","tid":2352114,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"食岩Macros，避免高糖就得<br />\n你唔係準備上台，唔駛咁緊張乜野食得乜野唔食得<br />\n最緊要係練夠食夠訓夠"},{"pid":"ecc1e93c51c98fcde40b9b86d63845877b30f2d6","tid":2352114,"uid":320041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60116e68c2681b26d9e275f795e2832a80b1d29e","tid":2352114,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:48:17.000Z","msg":"譚仔雞肉清湯<br />\n<br />\n味精多到你舉一世都無效果啦.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T19:57:21.000Z","msg":"真 清湯都勁高油同鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}